title: The Stranger (1960) Full Length Bonanza Western

sources.title: The Stranger (1960) Full Length Bonanza Western
sources.description:
The vengeful police inspector LeDuque (Lloyd Nolan) from New Orleans jeopardizes Ben's bid for the governorship over a twenty year murder.
 
Director: Christian Nyby
Writers: Oliver Crawford, Laurence Heath 
Stars: Lorne Greene, Pernell Roberts, Dan Blocker
Genres: Classics, Cult, TV, Western, Bonanza
